high_descs: Turn left, move to the fridge, turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, pick up the potato in the fridge.
Bring the potato to the microwave, right of the fridge.
Heat the potato in the mike.
Take the heated potato to the left, past the fridge, to the blue bin left of the fridge.
Put the heated potato in the blue bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the blue bin.

high_descs: Turn left and make your way to the fridge on the left
Take the potato out of the fridge
Turn around and step towards the stove, then turn left and step towards the counter then turn left
Microwave the potato then take the potato out of the microwave
Turn left, then turn right towards the fridge, then turn left and go past the fridge and turn right to face the blue container
Put the potato in the blue container
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato in the blue container next to the fridge

high_descs: Take a potato out of the fridge
Go to the bin next to the fridge
Place the potato in the bin
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in a bin
